As a Head Researcher I would like to create a questionnaire with questions with fixed choice answers so that I can gather quantitative data.
Labels: Deliver First (High Risk/High Value)
moscow: Must

Tasks
 A researcher is able to create a questionnaire
 Questionnaires can be created with custom titles
 The ability to create a question in which the user ticks from one of the provided options
 The ability to create a question in which the user ticks from multiple of the provided options
 The ability for the creator to specify the options
 Validation to ensure that the user cannot enter duplicate options
 The questions and options appear as expected
Bug Fixing
 Fix restricting duplicates.
 Fix restricting escaping unknown characters.
